==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Argo
<hw>Ar"go</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Argo</ets>, Gr. <?/.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Myth.)</fld> <def>The
name of the ship which carried Jason and his fifty-four companions to
Colchis, in quest of the Golden Fleece.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>A large constellation in the
southern hemisphere, called also <altname>Argo Navis</altname>. In
modern astronomy it is replaced by its three divisions,
<part>Carina</part>, <part>Puppis</part>, and
<part>Vela</part>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Argoan</ent>⟦br⟧
